 Trinity/Nightlight::
Trinity woke up and jumped around Aerotaur "Are you ok, Uncle Aerotaur???" said happily the girl" did you scared off all the mean bots??? why didn't you let me help you???? I'm a fearsome pred, uncle, I could have helped you"
Nightlight smiled and stopped near them.
